313
00:14:08,082 --> 00:14:09,021
ven?

314
00:14:09,432 --> 00:14:12,868
ven di krig, ven UNK zenen arayn di DEUTSCHEN.

315
00:14:13,313 --> 00:14:15,990
hot men oysgeshtelt ale mentshn in mark

316
00:14:16,401 --> 00:14:17,627
un

317
00:14:17,650 --> 00:14:20,361
⟨zey hobn gezen⟩ ver s'iz e- elter

318
