341
00:15:06,621 --> 00:15:07,593
in nayn

342
00:15:09,051 --> 00:15:11,002
vart tsu, lomikh nor gedenken.

343
00:15:13,692 --> 00:15:14,867
ven di krig

344
00:15:19,564 --> 00:15:22,967
ven m'hot shoyn ge- az zey hobn undz arayngegebn in di shnayderay

345
00:15:23,462 --> 00:15:24,772
tsu arbetn

346
00:15:25,690 --> 00:15:27,743
ven DEUTSCHEN zenen shoyn gevezn.

347
00:15:27,985 --> 00:15:29,987
nakher hobn zey gemakht a

348
00:15:30,921 --> 00:15:31,964
hobn zey

349
00:15:31,964 --> 00:15:33,530
