350
00:15:33,638 --> 00:15:36,180
zey hobn ⟨opgeCLEANED⟩. zey hobn aroysgenumen mentshn.

351
00:15:36,557 --> 00:15:40,351
hobn zey gekukt ver s'iz a- ver s'iz alt un ver s'iz yung.

352
00:15:40,351 --> 00:15:43,503
zey hobn gezen ver s'iz alt, hobn zey gelozt shteyn.

353
00:15:43,780 --> 00:15:47,368
ver s'iz alt hobn zey aroysgenumen, un di yunge hobn zey gelozt shteyn.

354
00:15:47,492 --> 00:15:50,574
hobn zey geshikt avek, un a sakh hobn zey geshosn

355
