359
00:16:00,553 --> 00:16:02,774
hobn zey gez- -lign oyf hey

360
00:16:02,815 --> 00:16:04,035
oyf der erd

361
00:16:04,035 --> 00:16:05,407
ale mentshn

362
00:16:05,970 --> 00:16:09,626
un nisht gehat keyn PLACE, gornisht, ⟨biz⟩ g-, m'hot zey nisht gegebn keyn esn

363
00:16:09,649 --> 00:16:10,875
biz zenen

364
00:16:11,016 --> 00:16:12,208
aroysgeganen

365
