381
00:16:48,698 --> 00:16:49,434
ye

382
00:16:49,558 --> 00:16:53,416
in Stashev, fun nayn un draysik biz dray un fertsik

383
00:16:50,419 --> 00:16:51,172
ye

384
00:16:53,203 --> 00:16:54,929
