386
00:16:58,229 --> 00:16:59,778
a gevise tsayt

387
00:16:59,886 --> 00:17:01,399
in, in geto?

388
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:02,243
in geto.

389
00:17:02,670 --> 00:17:06,950
