395
00:17:20,406 --> 00:17:22,037
zenen mir geven tsuzamen.

396
00:17:22,127 --> 00:17:25,192
vey- in di shnayderay veys ikh zenen mir gevezn

397
00:17:26,481 --> 00:17:29,107
un m'hot shoyn gehat zey avekgeshikt.

398
00:17:29,670 --> 00:17:32,954
m'hot shoyn gehat avekgeshikt. undz ze'mir nokh geven in di shnayderay.

399
00:17:34,210 --> 00:17:36,282
az ven iz dos letste m-

400
