in dray un fertsikstn yor. demolt hot men zey avekgeshikt.

402
00:17:43,744 --> 00:17:44,700
i-

403
00:17:45,651 --> 00:17:49,762
demo- oh, yetst gedenk ikh. in dray un fertsikstn yor hot men zey avekgeshikt

404
00:17:50,410 --> 00:17:53,188
iz, hot men undz gevolt mit zey geyn

405
00:17:53,818 --> 00:17:55,938
zenen mir aroysganen fun di LINE

406
00:17:56,232 --> 00:17:57,424
veyst a LINE?

407
00:17:57,514 --> 00:17:59,111
fun shure

408
00:17:59,708 --> 00:18:03,853
un m'hot gevolt geyn, hobn zey nisht gelozt, hobn zey geshlogn.

409
00:18:04,230 --> 00:18:08,291
hot mayn muter gezogt "kinder, ets zolt blaybn lebn

410
00:18:08,297 --> 00:18:10,265
ets zolt gedenken mayn nomen."

411
00:18:10,592 --> 00:18:12,901
un demo- un den iz zi avekgeganen.

412
00:18:12,901 --> 00:18:14,569
shoyn nisht mer gezen zey.

413
00:18:14,676 --> 00:18:15,682
keyn mol nisht.

414
00:18:15,537 --> 00:18:17,117
keyn mol nisht gezen.

415
00:18:16,785 --> 00:18:18,281
in dray un fertsik.

416
