428
00:18:44,038 --> 00:18:47,154
un undz hot men geshikt nokh Keltser HASAG demolt

429
00:18:47,548 --> 00:18:50,545
un nakher hot men undz geshikt nokh SKARZHISK.

430
00:18:50,670 --> 00:18:53,246
az keyn Kelts frier

431
00:18:53,387 --> 00:18:54,343
in Kelts

432
00:18:53,421 --> 00:18:56,655
