433
00:18:57,538 --> 00:18:58,409
NO

434
00:18:58,990 --> 00:19:00,705
shoyn nisht geven tsuzamen.

435
00:19:00,711 --> 00:19:03,821
bloyz mit eyn shvester bin ikh geven. tsvey

436
00:19:02,736 --> 00:19:03,810
mit velkhn

437
00:19:03,821 --> 00:19:05,801
tsvey. di vos iz do-hi

438
00:19:05,875 --> 00:19:07,928
