439
00:19:08,153 --> 00:19:10,374
do vos zi shteyt dort oyf di PICTURE.

440
00:19:11,292 --> 00:19:11,860
UNK

441
00:19:11,443 --> 00:19:12,331
dort oyf di

442
00:19:12,439 --> 00:19:13,293
oh, do

443
00:19:13,536 --> 00:19:15,167
