00:28:40,912 --> 00:28:42,875
ikh kon nisht, kon nisht visn genoy.

677
00:28:42,274 --> 00:28:44,751
nokh a mol etlekhe vokhn, monatn?

678
00:28:43,202 --> 00:28:45,609
az m'hot, m'hot geshikt, m'hot geshikt

679
00:28:45,632 --> 00:28:48,646
m'hot fun eyn PLACE undz geshikt tsum tsveytn

680
00:28:48,990 --> 00:28:52,598
kon ikh nisht gedenken, azoy in finef un fertsikstn yor zenen mir gevorn bafrayt

681
00:28:52,598 --> 00:28:54,907
vi kon ikh zogn di pinktlekhkeyt?

682
00:28:54,947 --> 00:28:58,268
pinktlekhkeyt ikh UNK nisht zogn UNK ⟨toyg dokh⟩ nisht. kon nisht gedenken.

